title: #LiveOutside2016 Watch 360º of Rio Artists Painting
description: Get a sense of what it’s like to work with street artists up on scissor lift as they hammer out the details on the mural. Check it out in 360 using the YouTube app or by clicking and dragging in Chrome on desktop. #LiveOutside2016
